<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="158" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="158">Supplemental description of female genitalia.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="158">Ovipositor simple: gonostylus with a very long apical seta, slightly longer than wide: distal gonocoxites elongated (Fig. 9c). Spermatheca connected in medial portion of vagina (Fig. 9c).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="158" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="158">Measurements</paragraph>
